OL,3,CReform unveil Senedd election
OL,4,Cmanifesto and pledge to scrap 20mph
OL,5,Cspeed limits
OL,7,FNigel Farage's party is launching what
OL,8,Fit calls a "blueprint for real
OL,9,Fchange", with pledges including
OL,10,Fscrapping default 20mph speed limits,
OL,11,Fdelivering an M4 relief road and
OL,12,Fupgrades on the A55, and scrapping the
OL,13,FLabour Welsh Government's Nation of
OL,14,FSanctuary policy, which aims to help
OL,15,Frefugees and asylum seekers placed in
OL,16,FWales by the UK Government to
OL,17,Fintegrate and access public services.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/6
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,467,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1772831165
OL,3,CReform unveil Senedd election
OL,4,Cmanifesto and pledge to scrap 20mph
OL,5,Cspeed limits
OL,7,FFarage and the party's Welsh leader
OL,8,FDan Thomas will unveil the manifesto
OL,9,Ftogether in Newport, where they will
OL,10,Fsay they plan to prioritise Welsh
OL,11,Fpeople for social housing, end the use
OL,12,Fof migrant hotels in Welsh
OL,13,Fcommunities, support the Welsh
OL,14,Flanguage, and announce a 5% council
OL,15,Ftax referendum limit.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/6
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
