PN,46604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1772831165
OL,3,CReform unveil Senedd election
OL,4,Cmanifesto and pledge to scrap 20mph
OL,5,Cspeed limits
OL,7,FAs for the NHS, Reform UK says it will
OL,8,F"reiterate that the Welsh health
OL,9,Fservice will always remain free, and
OL,10,Fpledge to slash waiting lists, end
OL,11,Fcorridor care and future-proof the NHS
OL,12,Fby upgrading hospitals and digital
OL,13,Finfrastructure".
OL,15,FThe Senedd election will take place on
OL,16,F7 May, with Reform polling in second
OL,17,Fplace behind Plaid Cymru.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/6
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
