SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1772831165
OL,3,CReform unveil Senedd election
OL,4,Cmanifesto and pledge to scrap 20mph
OL,5,Cspeed limits
OL,7,FParty leader Nigel Farage said: "I'm
OL,8,Fimmensely impressed by the hard work
OL,9,Fthat has gone into developing this
OL,10,Fambitious but realistic blueprint for
OL,11,Fgovernment.
OL,13,F"In a Senedd election campaign that
OL,14,Fhas been characterised by fantasy
OL,15,Feconomics from the other parties, this
OL,16,Fdocument is a serious plan to deliver
OL,17,Fthe real change Wales deserves.
OL,19,F"I look forward to campaigning
OL,20,Falongside Dan and the Welsh team
OL,21,Fbetween now and May 7."
OL,26,@oD@aOUuD@AOU{D@AOU}D@WO]
