OL,3,CReform unveil Senedd election
OL,4,Cmanifesto and pledge to scrap 20mph
OL,5,Cspeed limits
OL,7,FDan Thomas, Reform UK's leader in
OL,8,FWales, said: "This manifesto is a
OL,9,Fblueprint for real change here in
OL,10,FWales.
OL,12,F"These promises put Wales and Welsh
OL,13,Fcommunities first, and unlike the
OL,14,Fpledges put forward by other parties,
OL,15,Fthese are deliverable.
OL,17,F"Armed with this blueprint, we have
OL,18,Fall the building blocks to end a
OL,19,Fgeneration of decline here in Wales."
OL,26,@yD@AOU{D@eO]
